Huddled together with their arms around one another, these little monkeys look more than happy to pose for the camera.

The adorable images of the trio were taken at Jigokudani Monkey Park in Japan.

The attraction is a hotspot for tourists who visit the park in their droves to see the snow monkeys - also known as Japanese Macaques - bathing in the park's natural hot springs.

