So when husband-and-wife Chinping and
Yihfang Goh from Reading, UK, went to photograph the snow monkeys at 
the park they were more than happy to oblige.

The threesome had their arms wrapped around each other and pressed their little furry faces together for the photo.

They are are drawn to the welcoming waterhole to warm up during the winter.

